<!-- Fourth section - About the app -->
<div class="about-main-container">
<h2 id="main-header">About the app</h2>
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mr-4">
  <h5 class="text-justify mr-4" id="h5-spacing">Finally an app that allows you to get immediate feedback on any dilemma you're indecisive about. Engage with other users by voting, commenting or simply observing relatable dilemmas that others are facing. No dilemma is too small or big when we gather as a community to help each other decide.</h5>
  <p class="text-justify mr-4"><strong>A few guidelines to help you navigate the app. Dilemmas are categorized by complexity, which the user selects when creating a dilemma.</strong></p>
  <br>
  <p class="text-justify mr-4"><strong>Easy</strong> dilemmas stay active on the app for 24 hours.</p>
  <br>
  <p class="text-justify mr-4"><strong>Medium</strong> dilemmas stay active on the app for 3 days.</p>
  <br>
  <p class="text-justify mr-4"><strong>Hard</strong> dilemmas stay active on the app for 7 days.</p>
  <br>
  <p class="text-justify mr-4">Once archived, only the creator of the dilemma can view the dilemma in their profile page.</p>
  <p class="text-justify mr-4">Each dilemma allows you to vote or comment. You can upvote other comments as well. So post your first dilemma or start voting now!</p>
  </div>
</div>

